Rolling hills, vineyards and a magical Tuscany summer - everything came together to create the perfect setting for Hursh and Natasha’s wedding celebrations, surrounded by closest friends and family as they pledged their love to each other in one of the most romantic places on Earth! 
.
The celebrations kicked off with their crew - from laughter filled moments to cheering them every step of the way! What felt like a big happy family reunion resulted in some epic moments, and non-stop smiles! 
.
Here’s to a lifetime of adventure, laughter and joy for two incredible people who lit up a smashing few days in the heart of Tuscany!
